WEBVTT

00:00:09.663 --> 00:00:11.996
How does this music make you feel?

00:00:12.454 --> 00:00:14.121
Do you find it beautiful?

00:00:14.163 --> 00:00:15.788
Is it creative?

00:00:16.329 --> 00:00:17.954
Now, would you change your answers

00:00:17.996 --> 00:00:21.204
if you learned
the composer was this robot?

00:00:22.204 --> 00:00:23.454
Believe it or not,

00:00:23.496 --> 00:00:26.788
people have been grappling with
the question of artificial creativity,

00:00:26.829 --> 00:00:29.538
alongside the question
of artifcial intelligence,

00:00:29.579 --> 00:00:32.829
for over 170 years.